.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
\fBskool2html.py\fP [options] FILE [FILE...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
\fBskool2html.py\fP converts source skool and ref files to HTML. When FILE is
\(aq\-\(aq, \fBskool2html.py\fP reads from standard input.
